Set `ONA_TOKEN` in the environment before running Terraform:

```shell
export ONA_TOKEN="<api-token>"
terraform init
terraform plan
```

Set `ONA_HOST` only when your organization uses a non-default Ona host:

```shell
export ONA_HOST="https://<ona-hostname>"
```

